  "prompt": "How much should I expect to pay for a 1-car caltrain wrap advertisement?",
  "response": "The cost of a 1-car Caltrain wrap advertisement can vary based on several factors including the duration of the campaign, the specific location, and the size of the advertisement. Generally, prices for a full train car wrap can range from approximately $5,000 to $15,000 or more. It's advisable to contact Caltrain directly or work with an advertising agency that specializes in transit advertising to get an accurate quote tailored to your specific requirements and to inquire about any available options or promotional packages.",
